{"tid":2305301,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"挺侵律師鮑爾：中國、伊朗連上Dominion監控、操控美大選","createTime":"2020-11-29T13:42:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-30T03:15:50.000Z","uid":337052,"like":22,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c67c4bfa620893a3c58b0082f3f5658ec2e622bf","tid":2305301,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T13:42:38.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">挺川律師鮑爾：中國、伊朗連上Dominion監控、操控美大選</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n2020/11/29 21:18<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕<span class=\"red\">挺美國總統川普的律師鮑爾（Sidney Powell）週三（25日）提交訴狀，其中引述匿名網路安全專家的說法，指控中國、伊朗等境外勢力在美國大選期間連入了Dominion伺服器，監控、操控美國總統大選。</span>Dominion本週發布聲明，否認勾結外國勢力，也否認投票系統會用到USB記憶體，回應某位賓州聽證會上證人的證詞。<br />\n<br />\n據美國保守派媒體《Newsmax》報導，鮑爾律師在週三（25日）在密西根、喬治亞州提交的訴狀中，引述了一位做過軍事情報分析師的匿名證人的證詞，表示Dominion使用極易外洩的電腦身分驗證資訊，借助和外國敵對勢力有勾兌的伺服器和人員，有意無意地讓這些敵對勢力可以駭入投票資料庫，監控和操控選舉，2020的美國總統大選便深受其害。<br />\n<br />\n這位前軍事情報分析師是個經驗豐富的「白帽駭客」（white hat hacker），曾受僱於多個選舉領域的頂尖專家，運用駭客技術測試、破解、改善資訊系統安全性。在檢測之後，<span class=\"red\">他發現Dominion網路結點和數個境外勢力有聯繫：有人曾從中國湖南連入Dominion伺服器；除此，也追溯出某個伊朗網域的IP位置，而這意味著這些境外勢力事實上在美國大選期間連進了Dominion投票系統裡的選民名冊。</span><br />\n<br />\n這位匿名分析師總結：「Dominion完全無法提供一個基本的安全網路環境。」<br />\n<br />\nDominion本週稍早則發布聲明，否認有與外部勢力勾結，也表示他們的投票系統並不依賴網路、USB、或其他外接記憶體。Dominion關於外接硬碟的聲明，似乎是回應本週賓州聽證會上一位證人的證詞。據《福斯新聞》報導，那位證人曾親眼目睹有人在投票機插入好幾個USB卡，在沒有人監督的情況下上傳資料，<span class=\"red\">而賓州大選結束後，47個選務用的USB卡不見了。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3366032\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3366032&d=73P4J9mxZbud55ZbF8SGiV8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=a8b2089a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3366032&h=98c4ec91\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3366032</a>"},{"pid":"a408effea4cc2c2b7b0b1bc58449ea61511fb75c","tid":2305301,"uid":337052,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T13:44:16.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">Affidavit in Sidney Powell's Suit Claims Evidence Ties Vote Machines to Iran, China</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.newsmax.com/us/vote-machines/2020/11/27/id/999055/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsmax.com%2Fus%2Fvote-machines%2F2020%2F11%2F27%2Fid%2F999055%2F&d=73P4J9mxZbud55ZbF8SGiV8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=3c9aa1f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.newsmax.com/us/vote-machines/2020/11/27/id/999055/</a>"},{"pid":"f61aae3c68a30da6edc9f6e81eb0b947a5ecb2be","tid":2305301,"uid":265731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T13:45:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daa51378ad61a9698ce787a6d34e80a7ac4a0da8","tid":2305301,"uid":123264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T13:47:41.000Z","msg":"左膠 : 又fake news 我地中國同胞係無可能做D咁既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9448d419cfbe87e0a30e1089a034f731e759d68f","tid":2305301,"uid":1886,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T13:48:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WXm7PfN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWXm7PfN.png&h=24baa447&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n恭喜周庭和黃之峰<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2296813\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2296813</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"74cca743b776fa8f162898acd13c1cb607e3f7bb","tid":2305301,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T13:51:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/NetworksManager/status/1331781212508213251?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FNetworksManager%2Fstatus%2F1331781212508213251%3Fs%3D20&d=73P4J9mxZbud55ZbF8SGiV8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=735c5449\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FNetworksManager%2Fstatus%2F1331781212508213251%3Fs%3D20&h=25820424\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/NetworksManager/status/1331781212508213251?s=20</a>"},{"pid":"c452c00eca92258495c25a5094d10ab8f094ee72","tid":2305301,"uid":337052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T13:54:12.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">Pa. poll watcher, a Navy vet, alleges missing USB cards, up to 120,000 questionable votes</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.foxnews.com/politics/pa-poll-watcher-a-navy-vet-alleges-missing-usb-cards-up-to-120000-questionable-votes\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Fpa-poll-watcher-a-navy-vet-alleges-missing-usb-cards-up-to-120000-questionable-votes&d=73P4J9mxZbud55ZbF8SGiV8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=646b15f1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Fpa-poll-watcher-a-navy-vet-alleges-missing-usb-cards-up-to-120000-questionable-votes&h=063579a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.foxnews.com/politics/pa-poll-watcher-a-navy-vet-alleges-missing-usb-cards-up-to-120000-questionable-votes</a>"},{"pid":"06461ff87691bf9d2040759b1edb6ee7dff00b4d","tid":2305301,"uid":121146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T13:55:03.000Z","msg":"Dominion聲稱唔會用到usb  但州政府又話唔見usb  到底想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"553d3e401b639d99e5d12ab6e1fa3c5787a2c9f8","tid":2305301,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T13:58:42.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">前情報官作證：Dominion與中、伊、塞均有關聯</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/2020/11/28/a102997748.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ntdtv.com%2Fb5%2F2020%2F11%2F28%2Fa102997748.html&d=73P4J9mxZbud55ZbF8SGiV8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=15d45324\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/2020/11/28/a102997748.html</a>"},{"pid":"4dfeafed350fff789b2a05be2848efaeeb5f131e","tid":2305301,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T14:02:49.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">Sidney Powell to Newsmax TV: Dominion Contracts Warrant Criminal Probe</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.newsmax.com/newsmax-tv/sidney-powell-georgia-lawsuit-contract/2020/11/28/id/999106/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsmax.com%2Fnewsmax-tv%2Fsidney-powell-georgia-lawsuit-contract%2F2020%2F11%2F28%2Fid%2F999106%2F&d=73P4J9mxZbud55ZbF8SGiV8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=52c3aadc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.newsmax.com/newsmax-tv/sidney-powell-georgia-lawsuit-contract/2020/11/28/id/999106/</a>"},{"pid":"13b2e8846b9bebe38f7e9f240ad8dab5d9d0f60a","tid":2305301,"uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T14:03:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fKeNJHa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfKeNJHa.png&h=c224e9f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/itJCmuz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FitJCmuz.png&h=46a67ec0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gV0k3KV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgV0k3KV.png&h=43ca085b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qQte8ce.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqQte8ce.png&h=0b515182&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d0d89f2d0648c1637146efcae5c5528acaa5dc5e","tid":2305301,"uid":198071,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T14:10:02.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">大家知唔佩洛西係咩人？<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">合理懷疑Gphone班打手其中一個上司就係佩洛西，</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">佩洛西就係同共匪合作無間，<br />\n<br />\n修改美國大選結果，<br />\n<br />\n非法改選票，對抗特朗普，</span><br />\n<br />\n表面上做到同共匪敵對咁樣，<br />\n<br />\n實際上就係做盡破壞民主嘅嘢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-cv1L7ie7cY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-cv1L7ie7cY&d=73P4J9mxZbud55ZbF8SGiV8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=ca87cce7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-cv1L7ie7cY</a><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wksDgqj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwksDgqj.jpg&h=93ab8525&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港一直爭取普選幾十年都爭取唔到？<br />\n但2019年五大訴求就有機會爭取到？<br />\n當年貿易戰仲未有結果，大陸經濟仲未急速下滑，<br />\n究竟邊個咁有信心提出新嘅目標？<br />\n新目標嘅難道遠超過以前香港一直爭取嘅普選。<br />\n到依家全香港人嘅民主都受到侵犯。<br />\n<br />\n成個運動強調畫面靚，<br />\n係咁講俾人虐打嘅畫面可以爭取到西方嘅憐憫，<br />\n呢班人係咁推人出去根本就痴線。<br />\n<br />\n佢哋搞咁多嘢就係想軍隊合理入香港，<br />\n當初維利嘅軍隊喺深圳準備進入香港平亂，<br />\n如果唔係特朗普及時阻止，呢一場悲劇就會發生。<br />\n<br />\n當年黃之鋒係國教抗爭一事已經搞散過集會，<br />\n所以我對佢有少少保留，包括佢嘅組織。<br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒在獄中可以發布消息好唔不尋常，<br />\n<br />\n新疆好多真係爭取民主嘅人士都做唔到，<br />\n<br />\n如果真係要玩港式文藝勇武，<br />\n<br />\n都要等到特朗普連任成功，貿易戰取得顯著嘅成果，<br />\n<br />\n匪國經濟急速下滑，先好同人哋攤牌，當初根本冇攤牌嘅實力，<br />\n<br />\n竟然要犧牲大量香港人嘅生命作最後嘅反抗？得到乜嘢？"},{"pid":"232f40e497d708d0dd794cfa314204d3d62f1772","tid":2305301,"uid":198071,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T14:15:17.000Z","msg":"台灣人研究中共比香港人深入，也相信香港社運界一半已被滲透。<br />\n<br />\n當年黃毓民都係收國民黨錢，係共匪係透過國民黨俾錢佢。<br />\n<br />\n佢哋嘅資金來源，點解唔可以透過美國嘅內奸俾錢？<br />\n<br />\n佩洛西有資金來往嘅Dominion投票機公司跟深圳與香港有重大關聯<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.hkgolden.media/comment/2vgvlqfx.nevyrapuykn.lo45lx14qmf.knj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.hkgolden.media%2Fcomment%2F2vgvlqfx.nevyrapuykn.lo45lx14qmf.knj.jpg&h=19f28a63&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pi